dc_description_s: These line data layers represent trails for Burnett County, Wisconsin in 2017 and 2016. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Burnett_Trails_2017.gdb. The trail feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'BURNETT_GANDYDANCETRAIL_2017', 'BURNETT_SNOWTRAILS_2016', and 'BURNETT_SUMMERATVTRAILS_2016'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
